title: FNV Athlete Of The Week: D.J. Walton
text:
FNV Athlete Of The Week: D.J. Walton The Princess Anne running back scored 5 td's in the Cavs 60-21 win over Tallwood Post to Facebook FNV Athlete Of The Week: D.J. Walton The Princess Anne running back scored 5 td's in the Cavs 60-21 win over Tallwood   13newsnow.com: http://on.wvec.com/1RGlmvQ   Join the Conversation To   FNV Athlete Of The Week: D.J. Walton 10:02 p.m. EDT October 13, 2015 2 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE The junior running back had 5 first half touchdowns in the Cavs 60-21 win over Tallwood 
Our FNV Athlete Of The Week goes to running back D.J. Walton from Princess Anne High School. The junior with an efficient first half against Tallwood. He had 5 first half touchdowns as the Cavaliers rolled to a 60-21 win over the Lions. Walton also rushed for 134 yards and had 2 interceptions in the win. In the process, Princess Anne snapped an 11 game losing streak against Tallwood as they improved their record to 3-3. The Cavs also have their first 2 game win streak in 11 years.
